headline: On-The-Go Breakfast Packaging Market Report 2025 | Companies Focused on Leveraging Innovative Packaging Solutions to Meet Evolving Consumer Demands, Offering Promising Avenues for Growth
summary: The global on-the-go breakfast packaging market is projected to grow from $7.6 billion in 2024 to $10.59 billion by 2029, at a CAGR of 6.8%. Driven by rising disposable income, demand for sustainable options, and innovative packaging, key players like Amcor plc and Tetra Pak are leading the expansion.
